dct_title_s: China proper, NW 1:250,000 / prepared under the direction of the Chief of Engineers by the Army Map Service (PT).
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by form lines. Shows international, provincial, hsien, and territorial boundaries, roads, railways, masonry walls. Includes glossary, coverage, index to adjoining sheets and feet to meter conversion graph. Princeton University Library map collection has 32 sheets; see index. "Copied in 1945 from China 1:300,000, Central Land Survey, Ho-shui, 1935, Ch'ang-wu 1935; Lo-chu'an, 1935; Pai-shui, 1935."
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1945.
